### To create a new heroku link

https://github.com/Saurabh700/fake-restful-api

1. after cloning this repository just replace data in db.json
2. npm install
3. git status
4. git add .
5. git commit -m "msg"
6. git push origin master
7. heroku login
8. # Create the project
   heroku create your-api-project-name
9. # Deploy to Heroku
   git push heroku master
10. heroku open

### To update current heroku link

1. change data in db.json
2. git add .
3. git commit -m "msg"
4. git push origin master
5. git push heroku master

